#. Tag: title
#: details-widgets.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Widgets"
msgstr "Pripomočki"

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; has some specific widgets not found in other applications. The "
"usage of these widgets is explained in this chapter."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; ima nekaj posebnih pripomočkov, ki jih ni mogoče najti v drugih "
"aplikacijah. Uporaba teh pripomočkov je razložena v tem poglavju."

#. Tag: title
#: details-widgets.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid "Date entry and Date picker"
msgstr "Vnos datuma in izbirnik datuma"

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whenever &kmymoney; needs information about a specific date, &eg;, the "
"posting date of a transaction or the opening date of an account, it offers "
"the user the <emphasis>date entry widget</emphasis>. This widget consists of "
"three fields, which present the <emphasis>day</emphasis>, the "
"<emphasis>month</emphasis>, and the <emphasis>year</emphasis>, separated by "
"the date separator characters specified by your locale settings. If you push "
"the down arrow next to the date, the program will open the <emphasis>date "
"picker</emphasis> widget."
msgstr ""
"Kadarkoli &kmymoney; potrebuje podatke o določenem datumu, npr. datumu "
"knjiženja transakcije ali datumu odprtja računa, uporabniku ponudi "
"<emphasis>gradnik za vnos datuma</emphasis>. Ta pripomoček je sestavljen iz "
"treh polj, ki predstavljajo <emphasis>dan</emphasis>, <emphasis>mesec</"
"emphasis> in <emphasis>leto</emphasis>, ločena z ločilnimi znaki za datume, "
"ki jih določa vaš jezik nastavitve. Če poleg datuma pritisnete puščico "
"navzdol, bo program odprl gradnik <emphasis>izbirnik datuma</emphasis>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-widgets.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Date widget</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Gradnik datuma</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-widgets.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Date widget</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Gradnik datuma</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Within the date entry widget, the &Left;/&Right; cursor keys can be used to "
"switch between the <emphasis>day</emphasis>, the <emphasis>month</emphasis>, "
"and the <emphasis>year</emphasis> fields. Using the &Up;/&Down; cursor keys, "
"the value of the selected field can be incremented/decremented. The <keycap>"
"+</keycap> and <keycap>-</keycap> keys can be used to increment/decrement a "
"single day. Month and year boundaries are considered and incremented/"
"decremented if necessary. Pressing <keycap>T</keycap> will set the date to "
"today's date."
msgstr ""
"Znotraj gradnika za vnos datuma sta &Left;/&Right; s smernimi tipkami lahko "
"preklapljate med polji <emphasis>dan</emphasis>, <emphasis>mesec</emphasis> "
"in <emphasis>leto</emphasis>. Z uporabo smerni tipk &Up;/&Down;  lahko "
"vrednost izbranega polja povečate/zmanjšate. Tipki <keycap>+</keycap> in "
"<keycap>-</keycap> lahko uporabite za povečanje/zmanjšanje posameznega dne. "
"Mesečne in letne meje se upoštevajo in po potrebi povečajo/zmanjšajo. Če "
"pritisnete <keycap>T</keycap>, bo datum nastavljen na današnji datum."

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The date can also be changed using the mouse. Clicking on the <emphasis>day</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>month</emphasis>, or <emphasis>year</emphasis> field "
"selects the field. The value can then be incremented/decremented using the "
"&Up;/&Down; cursor keys. In addition, if you use the &Right;/&Left; cursor "
"keys, when you move to a different field, the entire field is selected, and "
"you can just type the new value for that field."
msgstr ""
"Datum lahko spremenite tudi z miško. S klikom na polje <emphasis>dan</"
"emphasis>, <emphasis>mesec</emphasis> ali <emphasis>leto</emphasis> polje "
"izberete. Vrednost lahko nato povečate/zmanjšate s tipkama &Up;/&Down; "
"smernimi tipkami. Poleg tega, če uporabljate smerne tipke &Right;/&Left; , "
"ko se premaknete na drugo polje, je izbrano celotno polje in lahko samo "
"vnesete novo vrednost za to polje."

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The date picker widget shows the currently selected month, name, and year. "
"Above that are four arrow buttons, two on each side of the displayed month "
"and year. The leftmost buttons are used to decrement the year and the month; "
"the buttons to the right of the year are used to increment the month and the "
"year. The button to the very right closes the date picker."
msgstr ""
"Pripomoček za izbiro datuma prikazuje trenutno izbrani mesec, ime in leto. "
"Nad tem so štirje puščični gumbi, dva na vsaki strani prikazanega meseca in "
"leta. Skrajni levi gumbi se uporabljajo za zmanjševanje leta in meseca; "
"gumbi na desni strani leta se uporabljajo za povečanje meseca in leta. Gumb "
"na desni strani zapre izbirnik datuma."

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Beneath the buttons, the widget presents a calendar page for the selected "
"month. Clicking a day on the calendar selects that date, closes the date "
"picker, and transfers the selected date into the <emphasis>day</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>month</emphasis>, and <emphasis>year</emphasis> fields."
msgstr ""
"Pod gumbi gradnik prikaže stran koledarja za izbrani mesec. S klikom na dan "
"na koledarju izberete ta datum, zaprete izbirnik datuma in prenesete izbrani "
"datum v polja <emphasis>dan</emphasis>, <emphasis>mesec</emphasis> in "
"<emphasis>leto</emphasis> ."

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the date picker widget, there are a button, a text edit "
"field, and a combo box. Pressing the button selects today's date in the date "
"picker. The text field can be used to enter a specific date. Pressing the "
"&Enter; key shows that date in the date picker widget. The combo box allows "
"the user to select a specific week, and continue to pick a date from there."
msgstr ""
"Na dnu pripomočka za izbiro datuma so gumb, polje za urejanje besedila in "
"kombinirano polje. S pritiskom na gumb izberete današnji datum v izbirniku "
"datuma. Besedilno polje lahko uporabite za vnos določenega datuma. S "
"pritiskom tipke &Enter; tipka prikazuje ta datum v gradniku izbirnika "
"datuma. Kombinirano polje omogoča uporabniku, da izbere določen teden in "
"nadaljuje z izbiro datuma od tam."

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case an invalid date is entered, the date picker will show a red frame, "
"and a tooltip will show details about the error."
msgstr ""
"Če je vnesen neveljaven datum, bo izbirnik datuma pokazal rdeč okvir, opis "
"orodja pa bo pokazal podrobnosti o napaki."

#. Tag: title
#: details-widgets.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "Value entry"
msgstr "Vnos vrednosti"

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The value entry widget consists of a text field (that accepts digits, "
"thousands separators, and decimal symbols) as well as a button to the right. "
"Use the digits to enter the value. Separate the fractional part by entering "
"the decimal separator for your locale. If you click on the button to the "
"right or press a key representing a numeric operation (&eg;, <keycap>+</"
"keycap>, <keycap>-</keycap>, <keycap>/</keycap>, <keycap>*</keycap> or "
"<keycap>%</keycap>) a little calculator will pop up and allow you to "
"calculate the final value."
msgstr ""
"Pripomoček za vnos vrednosti je sestavljen iz besedilnega polja (ki sprejema "
"števke, tisočice in decimalne znake) ter gumba na desni strani. Za vnos "
"vrednosti uporabite števke. Ulomek ločite tako, da vnesete decimalno ločilo "
"za svoj jezik. Če kliknete gumb na desni ali pritisnete tipko, ki "
"predstavlja številsko operacijo (&eg; <keycap>+</keycap>, <keycap>-</"
"keycap>, <keycap>/</keycap>, <keycap >*</keycap> ali <keycap>%</keycap>) se "
"bo pojavil majhen kalkulator, ki vam bo omogočil izračun končne vrednosti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Negative values can be entered by preceding the value with a minus sign. In "
"case your locale is set to display negative numbers with parentheses around "
"the value, the value can also be enclosed in parenthesis in the value entry "
"widget."
msgstr ""
"Negativne vrednosti lahko vnesete tako, da pred vrednostjo postavite znak "
"minus. Če so vaše področne nastavitve nastavljene tako, da prikazujejo "
"negativna števila z oklepaji okoli vrednosti, je lahko vrednost v oklepaju "
"tudi v gradniku za vnos vrednosti."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-widgets.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Value widget</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Gradnik vrednosti</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-widgets.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Value widget</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Gradnik vrednosti</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the calculator widget just like a normal calculator and once done leave "
"it by clicking on the <guibutton>=</guibutton> button or press the "
"<keycap>=</keycap> key on your keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Gradnik kalkulatorja uporabljajte tako kot običajni kalkulator in ga "
"zapustite tako, da kliknete gumb <guibutton>=</guibutton> ali pritisnete "
"tipko <keycap>=</keycap> na tipkovnici."

#. Tag: title
#: details-widgets.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Payee/Payer entry"
msgstr "Vnos prejemnika/plačnika"

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The widget for entering a Payee/Payer is very similar to a typical combo-"
"box, but has some additional features."
msgstr ""
"Gradnik za vnos prejemnika plačila/plačnika je zelo podoben tipičnemu "
"kombiniranemu polju, vendar ima nekaj dodatnih funkcij."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-widgets.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Payee widget</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Gradnik prejemnika plačil</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-widgets.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Payee widget</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Gradnik prejemnika plačil</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are requested to enter a payee/payer for a transaction, you can "
"start entering the name by pressing keys on your keyboard. As long as there "
"are entries in the list of payees/payers maintained by &kmymoney; which "
"match the characters entered, they will be presented in a box beneath or "
"above the text entry area. Using the mouse or the &Up;/&Down; keys, one can "
"select a name from that list. Using the keyboard additionally requires you "
"to select the entry by pressing the &Enter; key. Clicking the X to the right "
"of the entry area clears the field. Clicking the down arrow to the right of "
"the X displays the complete list of possible payees/payers."
msgstr ""
"Ko se od vas zahteva, da vnesete prejemnika plačila/plačnika za transakcijo, "
"lahko začnete vnašati ime s pritiskom tipk na tipkovnici. Dokler obstajajo "
"vnosi na seznamu prejemnikov/plačnikov, ki ga vzdržuje &kmymoney; ki se "
"ujemajo z vnesenimi znaki, bodo prikazani v polju pod ali nad območjem za "
"vnos besedila. Z uporabo miške ali tipk &Up;/&Down;, lahko izberete ime s "
"tega seznama. Uporaba tipkovnice dodatno zahteva, da izberete vnos s "
"pritiskom na tipko &Enter;. Če kliknete X na desni strani vnosnega območja, "
"počistite polje. S klikom na puščico navzdol desno od X se prikaže celoten "
"seznam možnih prejemnikov/plačnikov."

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a name is entered that is not yet known to &kmymoney; you will be asked "
"if you want to create a new payee/payer record. If you do not wish to do so, "
"then the field will be blanked. Otherwise, the record will be created and "
"added to the list."
msgstr ""
"Če je vneseno ime, ki ga &kmymoney; vprašani boste, ali želite ustvariti nov "
"zapis prejemnika/plačnika. Če tega ne želite storiti, bo polje prazno. V "
"nasprotnem primeru bo zapis ustvarjen in dodan na seznam."

#. Tag: title
#: details-widgets.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Category/Account entry"
msgstr "Vnos kategorije/računa"

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The field for entering a Category or Account is very similar to the one "
"described above for Payees/Payers."
msgstr ""
"Polje za vnos kategorije ali računa je zelo podobno tistemu, ki je opisano "
"zgoraj za prejemnike/plačnike."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-widgets.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Category widget</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Gradnik kategorije</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-widgets.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Category widget</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Gradnik kategorije</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-widgets.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To the right of the entry field, between the X for clearing it and the down "
"arrow for displaying the complete list, there is a split icon, which opens "
"the <link linkend=\"details.ledgers.split\">Split Editor</link>"
msgstr ""
"Desno od vnosnega polja, med X za brisanje in puščico navzdol za prikaz "
"celotnega seznama, je ikona razdelitve, ki odpre <link linkend=\"details."
"ledgers.split\">Urejevalnik razdelitev</link>"

